:"こころ","body":"あたし……？　今は学校の帰りよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"さっき一緒に歩いていた人はクラスメイトの人たち。\n最近、良くクラスの人たちに話しかけられるの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"今まであまり話したことのない人と話すのって楽しいわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"クラスメイトもだけど、学校は楽しいことが溢れているわね。\n香澄やイヴのような楽しくて笑顔が素敵な人もいるもの！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"他に楽しいこと？　そうね……学校以外だと、やっぱりバンドね！\n花音とはぐみ、薫、ミッシェルに美咲。\nみんなといると笑顔になるの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それが良く聞くバンドの魔法、なのかしら？\n良く分からないけど、良いことだわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"花音達とは演奏するだけじゃなくて、\n色んな人に笑顔を届けられるようなことを\n考えているの！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"ミッシェルはたまにしか練習には参加しないけど、\nきっとあたし達のことをいつも見ていてくれているんだわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それにミッシェルの代わりにいつも美咲がいてくれるわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"そうそう、さっき一緒に帰っていたクラスメイト達、\n実はこの前ライブに遊びに来てくれたの！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"色んな人にあたし達の音楽を聴いてもらえて、\nとても嬉しかったわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"クラスの人もあたし達の演奏を聴いて、\nハロハピが好きになったって言ってくれていたわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それにクラスメイトだけじゃない。\nライブの会場に来てくれた人もみんな笑顔になっていたわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"笑顔を忘れちゃった人も笑顔に出来ていたら、\nそれはとても良いことだと思うわよね！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"広がる笑顔といった感じかしら？　素晴らしいわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それで、さっき話したライブだけどね、\n実は美咲がやろうって言い出したの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"美咲はいつもはハロー、ハッピーワールド！　の\nサポートをしてくれているわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"何かを提案するより意見を整理したり、\nまとめてくれたりすることが多いの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"そんな美咲が真剣な顔をしてライブがしたいって言い出したの。\n何かあったのかしら？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"あたしはね、その言葉を聴いてすごく良いと思ったわ！\nあなたもそう思うでしょ？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"だって、美咲がやりたいって言ったの。\nそれを止める理由なんて何もないわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それにもしやらないって言ったら、\n美咲が笑顔じゃなくなっちゃうじゃない。\nそれは困るわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"だから、ライブをやることにしたの。\nライブに向けて新しい曲も考えたのよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"最初は薫の儚いをテーマにした曲にしようと思っていたけど、\n美咲は学校の人たちに伝えたいことがあるって言っていたわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それを聞いてね、だったらそれを歌にしようってなったの！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"伝えたかったことは、確か……考え方はいっぱいあるってこと！\nつまり、笑顔になるような曲よ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それでね、ライブでその曲を披露したら、すごかったのよ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"会場のお客さんが楽しそうに笑っていたわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"だからね、ライブをしようって言ってくれた美咲には\n感謝しないといけないわね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それだけじゃないわ。\n美咲はいつもライブする会場を探してくれるの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"人と交渉したり、そういうあたしには難しいことね。\nそれをいつも率先してやってくれるのが美咲なの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それだけじゃないわ。\nハロー、ハッピーワールド！　で決まったことを\nいつもミッシェルに伝えてくれているわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"いつも見えないところで頑張ってくれてるの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"最初はキグルミの人と思っていたけど、\n今はそうは思ってないわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"美咲は美咲よ。\nそれにハロー、ハッピーワールド！　には、\n美咲が必要だわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"それはそうと、少し気になっていることがあるのよ。\n美咲とミッシェルって声が似ている気がするのよね……\nねえ、そう思わない？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"そうよね！　それに口癖も同じ……ほどほど、だったわよね……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"他にも美咲に話したことをミッシェルが知ってたり、\nライブ中のことを美咲が知ってたりする……どうしてかしら？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"まるで、二人は通じ合ってるみたいよね……\n形はあんなに違うのに！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"あ……っ！　二人はもしかして……！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"すごく仲が良いのかしら？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"美咲、花音と仲が良いと思っていたけど、\nミッシェルとも仲が良かったのね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"あたしもバンドメンバーとして仲が良いことは嬉しいわ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"あら。少し話すつもりだったけれど、\nつい楽しかったことを全部話しちゃったわ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"楽しかったことを聞いてもらうと、\n笑顔だった時の気持ちを思い出してくるわよね！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"memorial187-04